question: Who has tablets and laptops with Windows 10?
sql_query1:
SELECT Students.FullName
FROM Students
WHERE (Students.Personal_Computing_Devices = "Tablet" OR Students.Personal_Computing_Devices = "Laptop") AND Students.Operating_System = "Windows 10"
sql_query2:
SELECT Students.FullName
FROM Students
WHERE Students.Personal_Computing_Devices = "Tablet" OR Students.Personal_Computing_Devices = "Laptop" AND Students.Operating_System = "Windows 10"
interpretation1: Show all the students who use either a tablet or laptop, where either runs on Windows 10.
interpretation2: Show all of the students who use a tablet, also show the students who use a latop running Windows 10.
